description: Progressive strength training based on Lance McCullough's proven methodology

phases.name: Max Determination Week
phases.description: Establish your baseline strength for personalized programming

weeks.title: Max Determination Week
weeks.goals: Establish maximum strength levels. Keep great form and be honest in your logging.

phases.name: Progressive Training
phases.description: Structured strength building with adaptive programming

weeks.title: Week 1 - Building Intensity
weeks.goals: Jump into the workout. Give it all you got and push to your limits every time.

weeks.title: Week 2 - Volume Focus
weeks.goals: Increase training volume with moderate weights and higher reps.

weeks.title: Week 3 - High Volume
weeks.goals: Continue to attempt new maxes and go for max repetitions.

weeks.title: Week 4 - Mixed Protocol
weeks.goals: Combine intensity and volume for balanced strength development.
